2101 typedef struct _ds3_client {
2102  ds3_str* endpoint;
2103  ds3_str* proxy;
2104  uint64_t num_redirects;
2105  ds3_creds* creds;
2106  ds3_log* log;
2107  ds3_error* (* net_callback)(const struct _ds3_client* client,
2108  const ds3_request* _request,
2109  void* read_user_struct,
2110  size_t (*read_handler_func)(void*, size_t, size_t, void*),
2111  void* write_user_struct,
2112  size_t (*write_handler_func)(void*, size_t, size_t, void*),
2113  ds3_string_multimap** return_headers);
